items.title: DoD tests AI models that make it easy to switch from vendors like Palantir
items.description: Investing.com -- The Department of Defense and other federal agencies have been testing AI models from Microsoft (NASDAQ:MSFT) and OpenAI specifically aimed at extracting data from analytics applications run by contractors like Palantir (NASDAQ:PLTR) and Lockheed Martin (NYSE:LMT), the Information reported on Monday.
